<h3>4.3.4 strategy_definitions：策略定义表</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th background-color="light-gray">字段</th><th background-color="light-gray">类型</th><th background-color="light-gray">约束</th><th background-color="light-gray">中文注释</th><th background-color="light-gray">枚举 / 备注</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
